This repository contains proprietary build tooling and configuration for
distributing third-party content packs. Build outputs (signed tarballs)
contain material from upstream projects under their own licenses;
consult each pack's install.meta.yaml and SBOM for upstream
attribution.

This repository is private and not offered for redistribution. A
stripped-down public mirror of the build tooling (without proprietary
configuration or non-redistributable pack inputs) may be published
separately under a permissive license. Until then, no rights are
granted to copy, modify, or distribute this repository's contents.
